name: Cry Me Some Pixel Gold
description:
"Ooh mighty Tezos, cry me some gold tis I'm so desperate to be sold!" said the NFT on Foundation to the Crused mysterious skull,
this skull was found in deep ruins of firey mountains by Nilfgardian soldiers after they pushed the elves away, in the second invasion, the ruins belonged to the ancient elves king dome, it had been said ...scavenging the ruins for gold, they found the cured skull and after it talked to them they started killing each ...
with its floating coin talked to him, the skull said to him that it could grant him anything with one exchange! his soul, and it did but the price was too high, eventually, the mages of the Emperor sealed the skull .... they offered it to the emperor, with the help of the mages it managed to bring lots of wealth to the empire! but such as the greed of men
it eventually made the emperor mad and led the whole empire to tremble and ruins! such it did to Elves, Dwarfs, and now waiting to be picked by another man.
